  <h2>General Setup</h2>
  <p>
    For any framework not listed above, add the tracking script to your HTML:
  </p>
  <pre><code>&lt;script src="https://your-domain.com/infinity.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
  Infinity.init(&#123;
    site_id: 'your-site-id'
  &#125;);
&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>Single Page Applications</h2>
  <p>For SPAs, track page changes manually:</p>
  <pre><code>// Track route changes
Infinity.track('page_view', &#123;
  path: window.location.pathname,
  title: document.title
&#125;);</code></pre>

  <p>
    Need help with a specific framework? <a
      href="mailto:support@getinfinitymetrics.com">Contact support</a
    >
  </p>
</DocsLayout>
